tachyon.master.lineage.meta

Class Lineage

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.master.lineage.meta.Lineage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JournalEntryRepresentable

    public final class Lineage
extends Object
implements JournalEntryRepresentable
    A lineage tracks the dependencies imposed by a job, including the input files the job depends on, and the output files the job generates.
